Generic:
  Group character separator: ___


Formatting options:
  [ ] Align equal signs

  [ ] Group keys
      Level deep: ___
      Insert ___ line(s) after each group.
      [ ] Align equal signs within group

  [ ] Wrap lines after ___ characters.
      ( ) Indent subsequent lines by ___ [spaces/tabs].
      ( ) Align begining of subsequent lines with equal sign.   	
